content:
The Stop Check Payment service process allows customers to cancel a check payment that hasn't been processed yet, for reasons such as theft or cancellation.

Available in: Lightning Experience, Professional, Enterprise, and Unlimited Editions where Financial Services Cloud is enabled.

To set up:

* Use the Service Process Studio to enable the Stop Check Payment service process.
* Capture and submit a stop check payment request through the Stop Check Payment OmniScript.
* A case is then created in Salesforce.
title: Stop Check Payment Service Process Setup and Management
